          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Audiobook " href="/book/show/16177515-the-lost-wife">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5009790-jessica?shelf=read-in-2013">read-in-2013</a>, 
