      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/15929266-the-lost-wife">Quotes from The Lost Wife</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;He laughs. And in his laugh I hear bliss. I hear feet dancing, the rush of skirts twirling. The sound of children.<br />Is that the first sign of love?<br />You hear in the person you're destined to love the sound of those yet to be born.&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
              &mdash;
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/quotes/507759-he-laughs-and-in-his-laugh-i-hear-bliss-i">50 likes</a>
            </nobr>
