          </div>
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;And I saw for the first time how, despite the isolation of our own lives, we are always connected to our ancestors; our bodies hold the memories of those who came before us, whether it is the features we inherit or a disposition that is etched into our soul.&rdquo;</span>
